    - rid: 2406609206760964809
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "\rI have no problem with anyone"
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964810
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Are you sure?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964811
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Okay, maybe I have small problem with those tiny creatures.

'
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964812
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Kill those monsters! There are 3 wolves. '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964813
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: They are looking like zombies sometimes, but it might be a bug.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964814
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 2406609206760964815
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 2406609206760964816
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 2406609206760964817
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Leave me alone...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964818
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I'm done with fighting.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964819
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, sorry for bothering your mighty head
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964820
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hey, i've heard that you may have some problem with wolves in forest?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964821
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Did you complete the task?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964822
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Please, leave me...

'
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964823
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay great... But...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964824
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You have this great sword and you said that you won't fight anymore
          so...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964825
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: So you want my sword? If yes, just say it.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964826
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Well, yes
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964827
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: There is no chance, but I can give you a wolf slayer. A spear whose
          owner was the most powerful slayer of wolf-like creatures in the forests.
          Of course, for a certain fee I can give it to you....
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964828
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Do you want "Wolf slayer spear"? '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609206760964829
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Fuck it, give it to me. *(pay 50gp)*\r"
    - rid: 2406609206760964830
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Nah, I preferred the sword so will thank you.
    - rid: 2406609206760964831
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'I don''t have enough money...

'
    - rid: 2406609206760964832
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Wow thanks, I didn't expect you to take this worthless.... I mean magical
          and invincible spear. Returns not accepted because.... It was used. Yes,
          it was used.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
