--- !u!114 &7313570313600629611
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e5800231a05eaae43b00503881229245, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  originalLanguage: en
  translationSets:
  - counter: 41
    languageCode: en
    translations:
    - id: 0
      language: en
      text: Scared barbarian
    - id: 1
      language: en
      text: "\rI have no problem with anyone"
    - id: 2
      language: en
      text: Jimbo
    - id: 3
      language: en
      text: Are you sure?
    - id: 4
      language: en
      text: 'Okay, maybe I have small problem with those tiny creatures.

'
    - id: 5
      language: en
      text: 'Kill those monsters! There are 3 wolves. '
    - id: 6
      language: en
      text: They are looking like zombies sometimes, but it might be a bug.
    - id: 7
      language: en
      text: Leave me alone...
    - id: 8
      language: en
      text: I'm done with fighting.
    - id: 9
      language: en
      text: Okay, sorry for bothering your mighty head
    - id: 10
      language: en
      text: Hey, i've heard that you may have some problem with wolves in forest?
    - id: 11
      language: en
      text: Did you complete the task?
    - id: 12
      language: en
      text: 'Please, leave me...

'
    - id: 13
      language: en
      text: Okay great... But...
    - id: 14
      language: en
      text: You have this great sword and you said that you won't fight anymore so...
    - id: 15
      language: en
      text: So you want my sword? If yes, just say it.
    - id: 16
      language: en
      text: Well, yes
    - id: 17
      language: en
      text: There is no chance, but I can give you a wolf slayer. A spear whose owner
        was the most powerful slayer of wolf-like creatures in the forests. Of course,
        for a certain fee I can give it to you....
    - id: 18
      language: en
      text: Narrator
    - id: 19
      language: en
      text: 'Do you want "Wolf slayer spear"? '
    - id: 20
      language: en
      text: "Fuck it, give it to me. *(pay 50gp)*\r"
    - id: 21
      language: en
      text: Nah, I preferred the sword so will thank you.
    - id: 22
      language: en
      text: 'I don''t have enough money...

'
    - id: 23
      language: en
      text: Wow thanks, I didn't expect you to take this worthless.... I mean magical
        and invincible spear. Returns not accepted because.... It was used. Yes,
        it was used.
    - id: 24
      language: en
      text: Wait, but you said this weapon is...
    - id: 25
      language: en
      text: It is the best! Unfortunately, you have a task, and now with this weapon
        you can complete it twice as fast.
    - id: 26
      language: en
      text: Ehhh, okay then. See you soon.
    - id: 27
      language: en
      text: For real? You really think that you can beat them without my mighty spear?
    - id: 28
      language: en
      text: Well... yes?
    - id: 29
      language: en
      text: Well, I was going to give it to you anyway
    - id: 30
      language: en
      text: Ohh, you poor man, I understand you. I once knew a white-haired warrior
        who was also robbed while drinking.
    - id: 31
      language: en
      text: Good luck my friend!
    - id: 32
      language: en
      text: '*(you gave him 50gp)*'
    - id: 33
      language: en
      text: Wolves are dead
    - id: 34
      language: en
      text: Great! As promised, here are three potatoes. See you around!
    - id: 35
      language: en
      text: I knew the spear would come in handy!
    - id: 36
      language: en
      text: No, I'm pretty sure I said it was a regular spear with a cool name.
    - id: 37
      language: en
      text: Go finish your task if you are not a coward.
    - id: 38
      language: en
      text: Not yet... I don't think this spear is what you said it was.
    - id: 39
      language: en
      text: Barbarian
    - id: 40
      language: en
      text: Thanks for help!!
